@startuml rankDescVec-读取路径-简化版
' ============================================================
' rankDescVec_ 读取路径简化时序图
' 基于 00-rankDescVec-6层读取链路时序图.puml 精简
' 目标：介绍大体流程，省略实现细节
' ============================================================

skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 40

title rankDescVec_ 读写路径 — 简化时序图

actor "调用者" as User

box "C API 层" #E8F5E9
    participant "HcclGetRankDescList" as Api
end box

box "V2/V1 分发" #FFF3E0
    participant "HCCLV2_FUNC_RUN" as Macro
end box

box "V2 框架层 (hccl 命名空间)" #E3F2FD
    participant "hcclComm\n+CollComm" as Framework
    participant "hccl::RankGraph\nV2 包装" as V2
end box

box "Legacy 实现层 (Hccl 命名空间)" #F3E5F5
    participant "IRankGraph\n接口适配" as IFace
    participant "Hccl::RankGraph\n数据源" as DataSrc
    database "rankDescVec_\nvector<RankDesc>" as Vec
end box

== Write Path - BuildRankDescVec ==

Framework -> DataSrc: BuildRankGraph() 阶段 8\nBuildRankDescVec(rankTable, globalRankIds)
activate DataSrc

DataSrc -> Vec: assign(count, RankDesc{})
DataSrc -> DataSrc: populate all 8 fields from rankTable and peers
DataSrc -> DataSrc: ReparseGroupedPlaneForOcsMesh ocsPlaneId ocsPlaneNum
DataSrc --> Framework: rankDescVec_ 就绪
deactivate DataSrc

== Read Path - V2 Query ==

User -> Api: HcclGetRankDescList(comm, &descList, &descNum)

Api -> Api: 参数校验 (CHK_PTR_NULL x3)

Api -> Macro: HCCLV2_FUNC_RUN(lambda)
Macro -> Macro: hrtGetHcclV2Support() == true
note over Macro: 执行 lambda 并 return

Api -> Framework: GetCollComm()->GetRankGraph()
Framework --> Api: hccl::RankGraph* (= RankGraphV2)

Api -> V2: GetRankDescList(descList, descNum)
activate V2

V2 -> IFace: pImpl->GetRankDescList(...)
activate IFace

IFace -> DataSrc: GetRankDescVec()
activate DataSrc
DataSrc --> IFace: const vector<RankDesc>&
deactivate DataSrc

IFace -> IFace: *descList = const_cast(vec.data())\n*descNum  = vec.size()

IFace --> V2: HCCL_SUCCESS
deactivate IFace

V2 --> Api: HCCL_SUCCESS
deactivate V2

Api --> User: HCCL_SUCCESS\n  descList points to rankDescVec_ data\n  descNum = total rank count

== V1 Fallback - device not support V2 ==

User -> Api: HcclGetRankDescList(...)
Api -> Macro: HCCLV2_FUNC_RUN(lambda)
Macro -> Macro: hrtGetHcclV2Support() == false
note over Macro: lambda 不执行，控制流继续到 V1 代码
Api --> User: HCCL_E_NOT_SUPPORT

@enduml
